THE CONTRACT COMPLETION DATE WILL BE EXTENDED FROM DECEMBER 30, 2016 TO JANUARY 31, 2017. IT IS AGREED THAT THE EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT PROVIDED FOR IN THIS MODIFICATION CONSTITUTES AN ACCORD AND SATISFACTION OF ANY AND ALL PAST, PRESENT AND FUTURE CLAIMS FOR ADDITIONAL MONETARY COMPENSATION AND TIME FOR THE ACCOMPLISHMENT OF THE WORK DESCRIBED IN THIS MODIFICATION.
